[I] A NeXT computer hardware emulator

[T] Previous is a NeXT computer hardware emulator. It runs all versions of
[T] the NeXT operating system from NeXTstep 0.8 through OPENSTEP 4.2.

[U] http://previous.alternative-system.com/

